comment._content: Accompanying note: "Members of the Thanksgiving Basket Committee of Delta Sigma Theta Sorority's Gamma Eta Sigma Chapter are shown just prior to making the distribution of food to needy families in the community Wednesday evening. Kneeling, left, Miss[?] Flossie[?] Boyd[?] chariman; Mrs. Minnie Fields and Mrs. Gladys Anderson. Standing, left, Mrs. Dorothy O. Holmes, Miss Lucy Rose Adams, Miss M. Lucie James, Mrs. Mary Hall, and Miss Genise[?] Lowe, president."
comment.authorname: State Library and Archives of Florida
